'''卡迪夫城2009年至2010年球季'''是[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]在[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英格蘭足球聯賽]]第83個球季，亦是於2003年透過附加賽自[[英格蘭足球聯賽|乙組聯賽〈第三級〉]]升班後連續第7個處於第二級聯賽的球季，上季以第7位結束球季。球隊本季由使用了99年的[[尼尼安公園球場|尼尼安公園球場]]（Ninian Park）遷入新建的[[卡迪夫城運動場|卡迪夫城運動場]]（Cardiff City Stadium）。

== 記事 ==
* 2009年7月22日新建價值5,000萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]的[[卡迪夫城運動場|卡迪夫城運動場]]（Cardiff City Stadium）啟用，由[[加的夫|卡迪夫]]市議會領袖朗尼·伯曼（Rodney Berman）主持揭幕<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/wales/8162855.stm |title=£50m Cardiff City Stadium opens |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2009-07-22 |accessdate=2009-07-26 |archive-date=2020-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204100355/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/wales/8162855.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，首場[[友誼賽|友賽]][[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:凯尔特人;zh-hk:些路迪}-]]0-0和氣終場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8164021.stm |title=Cardiff City 0-0 Celtic |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-07-22 |accessdate=2009-07-26 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413080808/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8164021.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。
* 2010年5月27日球會股東接受[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]財團注資600萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]換取約30%股權，牽頭人曾長義（Datuk Chan Tien Ghee）獲委擔任主席<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8706910.stm |title=Cardiff City's £6m Malaysian investment approved |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-05-27 |accessdate=2010-07-01 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124072459/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8706910.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

==球衣==
2009年6月26日卡迪夫城宣佈與[[PUMA|彪馬]]（Puma）簽訂五年球衣供應合約，採用「創世記集團國際」（Genesis Group International）授權製造的高科技球衣<small><ref name="Puma">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.cardiffcityfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10335~1704281,00.html |title=City and Puma Pen Five Year Deal |publisher=[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|''cardiffcityfc.co.uk'']] |date=2009-06-30 |accessdate=2010-04-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100802123925/http://www.cardiffcityfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10335~1704281,00.html |archivedate=2010-08-02 }}</ref></small>，這間以[[德國|德國]]為總部的公司曾於2002至2005年為球隊供應球衣三年<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.historicalkits.co.uk/Cardiff_City/Cardiff_City.htm |title=Cardiff City |publisher=historicalfootballkits.co.uk |accessdate=2009-07-16 |archive-date=2017-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917080434/http://historicalkits.co.uk/Cardiff_City/Cardiff_City.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

開季首7場賽事未有球衣[[贊助|贊助]][[廣告|廣告]]，直到9月11日球會才公告與[[亞洲|亞洲]]網上遊戲及博彩公司「777ball.com」達成合作協議<small><ref name="777ball.com">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2009/09/11/cardiff-city-land-250k-shirt-sponsor-91466-24660003/ |title=Cardiff City land 250k shirt sponsor |publisher=''South Wales Echo'' |date=2009-09-11 |accessdate=2009-09-11}}</ref></small>，但僅穿上新贊助球衣作賽一場後，才發覺贊助商沒有領取在[[歐洲|歐洲]]發放廣告的牌照，其[[商標|商標]]隨即在球衣上被移除<small><ref name="nosponsor">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/wales/south_east/8260805.stm |title=Sponsor removed from City shirts |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2009-09-17 |accessdate=2009-09-21}}</ref></small>。9月28日球會宣佈找到替代贊助商，與博彩公司「SBOBET」簽署兩年贊助合約<small><ref name="SBObet">{{Cite web |language=en |url=http://www.cardiffcityfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10335~1810688,00.html |title=SBOBET.com: City's new sponsor |publisher=cardiffcityfc.co.uk |date=2009-09-28 |accessdate=2009-08-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090930222804/http://www.cardiffcityfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10335~1810688,00.html |archivedate=2009-09-30 }}</ref></small>。

